## Emphasis Legend

Markers preserved from Jira source. Agents on subsequent phases MUST respect these:

| Marker | Source | Semantic |
|--------|--------|----------|
| `**🔴 CRITICAL:** X` | Jira `{color:red}X{color}` | Non-negotiable directive, cannot be interpreted/narrowed by agent. Must map to CRITICAL-severity FR with explicit `[WAIVED: {Jira quote or comment ref}]` if excluded. |
| `**🟠 WARNING:** X` | Jira `{color:orange}X{color}` | Strong emphasis, should be preserved in FR unless explicit waiver. |
| `**X**` (bold) | Jira `*X*` | Emphasis from reporter, priority hint for FR coverage. |
| `X!!!` or `X!!` | Jira literal `!!!` | Reporter-level emphasis, treat as STRONG CRITICAL. Agent MUST NOT add open question contradicting text with `!!!`. |
| `*X*` (italic) | Jira `_X_` | Nuance/clarification, optional trace. |

